ldaSegmentation:
Will not work unless certain source files are present

Original code can be found here: https://github.com/cudbg/Dialectic

The idea was to create a pipeline that gave user’s real time feedback while they wrote reviews for items they had purchased, in our case the items was restricted to laptops.

Please look at the readMe inside of ldaSegmentation for information as to how the code works
